<view class="page">
  <view class="intro">
    按广告位类型填写投放天数与赠送天数（赠送不填视为 0）。到期日 = 投放起始日 + 投放天数 + 赠送天数；首次填写时起始日默认为保存当日。将同步到该客户名下该类型的全部广告位。
  </view>
  <view class="client-hd">
    <text class="client-name">{{clientName}}</text>
  </view>

  <block wx:for="{{typeRows}}" wx:key="type">
    <view class="type-card">
      <view class="type-row">
        <text class="type-label">{{item.type}}</text>
        <text class="type-clear" data-index="{{index}}" bindtap="onClearType">清除</text>
      </view>
      <view class="days-row">
        <view class="days-cell">
          <text class="days-label">投放天数</text>
          <input
            class="days-input"
            type="number"
            placeholder=""
            value="{{item.placementDays}}"
            data-index="{{index}}"
            data-field="placementDays"
            bindinput="onDaysInput"
          />
        </view>
        <view class="days-cell">
          <text class="days-label">赠送天数</text>
          <input
            class="days-input"
            type="number"
            placeholder=""
            value="{{item.bonusDays}}"
            data-index="{{index}}"
            data-field="bonusDays"
            bindinput="onDaysInput"
          />
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="expire-preview">
        <text class="expire-preview-k">到期日期</text>
        <text class="expire-preview-v {{item.expirePreview ? '' : 'is-placeholder'}}">
          {{item.expirePreview || '填写投放天数后自动计算'}}
        </text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </block>

  <button class="btn-save" bindtap="saveAll">保存并同步</button>
</view>
